<h2 class="bold font-l">You got to Wear a Uniform.</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Knowing that he will be fighting against his best friend, Steve opts to steal his old WWII Uniform which was put on display inside of the Smithsonian. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/StrippingTheScarecrow" class='trope-example-link'>Stripping the Scarecrow</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
