<p><span class="bold">Stan Lee [Capta...</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="iyylco" data-video-descrip="Avengers: Endgame pays homage to Cap's epic elevator ass-kicking (but with a surprise twist)!" data-video-title="Cap's Elevator Homage" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/iyylco_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/caps_elevator_homage_moment2.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/InternalHomage" data-video-tropename="Internal Homage" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Film/CaptainAmericaTheWinterSoldier,Characters/MCUHYDRAOperatives,Film/AvengersEndgame,Characters/MCUCaptainAmerica" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/caps_elevator_homage_moment2.jpg">
